Still loved, still missed and very dear"Ę
┤L.H.R ALLEN
COVENTRY
1909 - 1998
In memory of L.H. Allen,
and his wife Connie (1910 - 2000).
With gratitude - 
their daughters, and sone.
'As Coventrians, they valued this Park!'
And in memory of their daughter.
Pauline Allen (1944 - 1991).
With affection - 
her sisters, and brother,
and friends"╠
